Package eu.excitement.entailment.core.utilities.immutable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImmutableCollection<T>
    A collection with only operations that make no changes on the collection.
    ImmutableList<T>
    List, like java.util.List , but has no operation that changes the list.
    ImmutableMap<K,V>
    Represents an immutable map.
    ImmutableSet<T>
    Much like java.util.Set but only with "read" operations.

    EmptyIterator<E>

    A simple implementation of ImmutableSet.
